table_description: AWS S3 Bucket Intelligent Tiering Configuration

columns.name: bucket_name
columns.description: The name of the container bucket of this object.

columns.name: id
columns.description: The ID used to identify the S3 Intelligent-Tiering configuration.

columns.name: status
columns.description: Specifies the status of the configuration.

columns.name: tierings
columns.description: Specifies the S3 Intelligent-Tiering storage class tier of the configuration.

columns.name: filter
columns.description: Specifies a bucket filter. The configuration only includes objects that meet the filter's criteria.
